#- The Nyational Workers’ Party was founded with the purpose to preserve and expand the glory of Nyasaland. The party was founded out of the Nyasaland Fascist Party as it was reorganized into a new party under the unified leadership of BennyZ and cat_alunya
#- Immigration:§0
§0In order to be a strong and competitive nation on the international scale, we require a much larger population than we currently have. Hence we will embrace immigrants and help them integrate in to our culture.
#- Expansionism:§0
§0In order to have enough space for the workers of Nyasaland, we require living space. The NWP will push for expanding the borders of Nyasaland.
#- Populism:§0
§0The Nyational Workers’ Party believes that the will of the workers should be the primary goal of the rulers of Nyasaland. If any ruler be it minor or major isn’t pushing the interests of the workers they will be dealt with.
#- Revolution:§0
§0The Nyational Workers’ Party believes that revolution is a powerful tool that is only to be used in the most extreme cases. Revolutions always cause workers to fight other workers instead of expanding the nation. But if the direction that the
#- leadership is taking is pacifying us then this tool is very valuable.
#- Militarism:§0
§0Our ultimate goal is to see Nyasaland become powerful. This cannot happen without a strong military to defend our territory and our workers. 
#- Independence:§0
§0The Nyational Workers’ Party were the ones that helped our glorious country to independence and will keep us independent from any who wish to enslave us again.
#- Civ Servers:§0
§0The Nyational Workers’ Party has decided that Devoted 3.0 was the best Civ server and any opposition to this is just cause for expulsion from the party and Nyasaland.
#- 